      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BABY YOSHI (2) has been in the frame at her last two runs, most recently when third (23.56) in a Bottom Up - Grade 7 over 400m at Warragul. Can turn form around here. ASTON ANTIBES (7) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at this track behind Nala's Girl (20.61) in a T3 Grade 7. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Can feature again. PAW EZRA (8) is having her first look at this track. Comes here a last start placegetter at Shepparton in a T3 RSTW (22.83). Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from four starts. Bold showing expected. WARRIOR LIZZY (3) is new to this circuit but warrants respect.",
